16 REPEALING SECTIONS 1 THROUGH 9, CHAPTER 509, LAWS OF 2021; AND PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE
17 EFFECTIVE DATE AND A RETROACTIVE APPLICABILITY DATE.”
